            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThese%20three%20little%20words-our%20God%20approaches-are%20the%20most%20certain%20fact%20in%20the%20universe.%20We%20may%20be%20going%20through%20terrible%20trials%2C%20tribulations%2C%20sufferings%2C%20and%20temptations%2C%20but%20we%20can%20be%20certain%20of%20one%20thing%3A%20our%20God%20is%20coming!%20One%20day%20Christ%20will%20return%20to%20earth.%20A%20fire%20will%20devour%20before%20Him%20(v.%203)%20as%20He%20returns%20to%20destroy%20the%20Antichrist%20and%20his%20armies.%20God%20Himself%20will%20be%20the%20Judge%20of%20His%20people%20(v.%206).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20concept%20of%20Jesus'%20return%20took%20center%20stage%20as%20Christ%20taught%20His%20disciples%20about%20the%20end%20of%20time.%20%22However%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20the%20day%20or%20hour%20when%20these%20things%20will%20happen%2C%20not%20even%20the%20angels%20in%20heaven%20or%20the%20Son%20himself.%20Only%20the%20Father%20knows%22%20(Mark%2013%3A32).%20Since%20we%20cannot%20know%20the%20moment%20of%20His%20return%2C%20we%20must%20remain%20diligently%20on%20our%20guard%2C%20for%20His%20arrival%20could%20be%20%22at%20evening%2C%20midnight%2C%20early%20dawn%2C%20or%20late%20daybreak%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(v.%2035).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAs%20we%20battle%20the%20enemy%2C%20we%20should%20be%20constantly%20looking%20skyward%20for%20the%20imminent%20return%20of%20our%20Lord.%20Focusing%20on%20His%20coming%20will%20keep%20us%20on%20guard%20against%20sin%2C%20compromise%2C%20and%20slothfulness%20and%20will%20encourage%20us%20in%20battle.%20We%20must%20keep%20our%20lives%20equipped%20and%20our%20hearts%20ready%2C%20because%20there%20will%20be%20no%20time%20for%20preparation%20at%20His%20sudden%20return.%20To%20the%20sleeping%2C%20distracted%2C%20halfhearted%20Christian%2C%20Jesus%20gives%20one%20word%20that%20will%20keep%20him%20on%20track%20for%20life%3A%20%22Watch!%22%20(Mark%2013%3A37).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
